Test Scenarios to check only the integration part between Product details screen and cart screen in any e-comm application (Shopee)
Check product details
Given User already at app homepage
When User tap the search field
And User type the keyword to search a product that want to buy
And User click product column
Then System will shown product details page
When User click "Add to Cart" button
And User click the add-ons
And User click "Add to Cart" button at the buttom of pop up
Then The product will successfully added to cart

Check cart screen
Given User already add some product to cart
When User click "Cart" icon
Then System will navigated to cart page
And System will show list of product that have been added
